author-identifier-system error QuestionnaireResponse.author.identifier.system QuestionnaireResponse.author.identifier.system must be 'http://dsf.dev/sid/organization-identifier' or 'http://dsf.dev/sid/practitioner-identifier' $this = 'http://dsf.dev/sid/organization-identifier' or $this = 'http://dsf.dev/sid/practitioner-identifier'

author-if-completed-or-amended error QuestionnaireResponse Author must be set if QuestionnaireResponse.status equals completed or amended ((%resource.status = 'completed' or %resource.status = 'amended') implies author.exists()) and ((%resource.status = 'completed' or %resource.status = 'amended') implies author.identifier.exists())
authored-if-completed-or-amended error QuestionnaireResponse Authored must be set if QuestionnaireResponse.status equals completed or amended (%resource.status = 'completed' or %resource.status = 'amended') implies authored.exists()
dom-2 error QuestionnaireResponse If the resource is contained in another resource, it SHALL NOT contain nested Resources contained.contained.empty()

qrs-1 error QuestionnaireResponse.item, QuestionnaireResponse.item:user-task-id, QuestionnaireResponse.item:business-key, QuestionnaireResponse.item:@default Nested item can't be beneath both item and answer (answer.exists() and item.exists()).not()
